language.item:
You will now be asked about how far you agree or disagree with 15 statements about how urban
        green and blue space affects your personal health and wellbeing.
        {br}{br}
        There are three steps:{br}{br}
        {ol}
        {li}Read each of the 15 statements and allocate them into one of three boxes – Agree, Disagree or Neutral. You
        can click and drag each statement.{/li}
        {li}Review the contents of each of your three boxes and decide which you most strongly agree and disagree with.
        Click and drag the statements into one of five more specific categories.{/li}
        {li}Complete a few questions about yourself and submit. When you submit your responses you will be able to see
        the statements that you most agreed and disagreed with mapped at your postcode. You will also be able to see
        what other people thought.{/li}
        {/ol}
        {p}Please maximize your browser window and click on the continue button to start the survey.{/p}

Read the following statements carefully and split them up into three piles:{br}{br}
