        {li}a pile for statements you tend to disagree with, {img src="img/disagree.png"}{br}{/li}
        {li}a pile for cards you tend to agree with, {img src="img/agree.png"} and{br}{/li}
        {li}a pile for the neutral ones {img src="img/neutral.png"}{/li}
        {/ul}{br}{br}
        You can either drag the cards into one of the three piles or press 1, 2, 3 on your keyboard. Changes can be made
        later.{br}{br}
        If you want to read this instruction a second time, press the help button at the bottom right corner.

